Information About QuickTake SoftwareThe Macintosh software for the QuickTake 100 has two separate installs: one for 68k, and another for PowerPC computers. It is not compatible with System Software 7.5.3.The Macintosh software for the QuickTake 150 is compatible with all current System Software versions and is backwards compatible with the QuickTake 100.Version 1.5 of the Windows software for the QuickTake 150 is also backwards compatible with the QuickTake 100.